{"about_the_game":"<strong>SpaceKraft is a physics based spaceship simulation which you craft elements and explore the open world.</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/Header_New.gif?t=1726593004\" /><br><br><strong>Docking Arm and Crane Rope</strong><br>Spaceship has a docking arm to hold and move objects precisely and a crane rope in the back to lift objects from planet surfaces.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/Docking_Arm.gif?t=1726593004\" />  <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/Crane_Rope.gif?t=1726593004\" /><br><br><strong>Crystals and Upgrades</strong><br>You can collect crystal energy to refuel, repair or upgrade your spaceship. Afterburner, armor, extra fuel tank, reinforced chassis and more...<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/Collect_Crystal.gif?t=1726593004\" /> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/Upgrade.gif?t=1726593004\" /><br><br><strong>Run Generators</strong><br>In addition, crystals can be used to power generators that activate various machines or stations, which can be helpful in situations such as teleporting to another planet or sending an emergency signal for assistance.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/Generator_Run.gif?t=1726593004\" /> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/Repair_Cable.gif?t=1726593004\" /> <br><br><strong>Planets</strong><br>As you explore new planets, you can discover more resources to gather. Craft further elements to repair facilities. Each planet has its own unique features.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/Rock_Removal.gif?t=1726593004\" /> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/Other_Planets.gif?t=1726593004\" /><br><br><strong>Story</strong><br>Tom, our hero, finds himself abducted into an unknown universe where he must navigate through the strange new world, uncover the secrets of his abduction, and ultimately find a way back home to planet Earth.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/Intro_Anim.gif?t=1726593004\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1726593004","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1726593004","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1726593004","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1726593004","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<strong>SpaceKraft is a physics based spaceship simulation which you craft elements and explore the open world.</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/Header_New.gif?t=1726593004\" /><br><br><strong>Docking Arm and Crane Rope</strong><br>Spaceship has a docking arm to hold and move objects precisely and a crane rope in the back to lift objects from planet surfaces.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/Docking_Arm.gif?t=1726593004\" />  <img class=\"bb_img\